{"tid":1865054,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[集運速遞無限輪迴] 網購口罩集運討論2","createTime":"2020-02-06T03:20:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T09:14:12.000Z","uid":337604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"27fbdd6d4937dbfa91f37694ef89da3d307a1099","tid":1865054,"uid":337604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T03:20:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><em>內容及資料僅供參考，投資涉及風險，口罩價格可升亦可跌，甚至變成亳無價值。投資者在決定是否購買有關口罩之前應先閱讀有關風險評估，以了解該建議發售之詳細資料，並應就本身的財務、其他狀況及需要，詳細考慮並決定購買有關口罩是否切合本身特定的需要，若有需要更應咨詢其他專業意見，方可作出有關購買決定。<br />\n忠告：親自買罩 咪俾錢炒狗</em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n間間集運都爆，唔好再問邊間快啲邊間好用，根本就無人知。記得留意返集運公司對體積重收費同要求，隨時運費貴過口罩本身，重有拒收嘅風險存在。<br />\n<br />\nAmazon自己送<br />\nKatolec=老人<br />\nYamato=貓<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>麻煩大家Amazon唔好再用殘體字 有得揀英文/日文</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zsq6yyZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fzsq6yyZ.jpg&h=8752b55a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd25d24a6c26d52df165c9fd68329a98fe577e3","tid":1865054,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T03:21:04.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce07cac2772f1832de3256d880abf576b7ca3264","tid":1865054,"uid":307698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T03:22:53.000Z","msg":"今朝啲骨送左去到貨啦個東京倉，黑貓又無寫係唔係比左front desk，到底我啲骨到左個倉未<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a100070d2984f14fd288f5a45fdf9d77b784dc1","tid":1865054,"uid":172213,"like":0,"di